settings.heading: How Much Does Shipping Cost?
settings.txt:
Shipping rates vary depending on location.

USA:$8.99per box.
Canada:$14.99per box
Worldwide: Various -please see this articlefor a list of international rates.

The shipping cost is PER BOX. If you purchase the 3-Month Plan shipped within the US, you will be charged $86.98 USD for the subscription and 3 x $8.99 USD for shipping.

** Please note: The above, fixed shipping rates are for our regular monthly subscription boxes. For any past boxes, books and items purchased through the shop, shipping will be calculated at checkout. **

All prices are inUSD. Any applicable State, Provincial or National (UK VAT, AUS GST, etc) taxes are applied at checkout.

settings.heading: How Do I Update My Payment Details?
settings.txt:
To update your payment details, you just need to log into your OwlCrate customer account and click the Billing Information tab on your main account page. This will take you to a page where you will see your Card On File and Billing Address listed.

Click UPDATE CARD and you will be able to fill in a new card form.

Confirm by hitting the UPDATE CARD button at the bottom of the form and you will be good to go!

For step-by-step instructions, please visit ourHelp Centre.

settings.heading: How Do I Update My Shipping Address?
settings.txt:
To update your address, you just need to log into your customer account through owlcrate.com and clickMANAGE SUBSCRIPTIONSorMy Subscriptions.

On the next page, you can expand the active subscription box by clicking the[+].You will then see a teal[>]next to your current address. When you click that arrow, a window will open so you can enter your new shipping address. To confirm, clickUPDATE SHIPPING ADDRESS.

Note: Be sure to update your shipping address before your renewal goes through on the 1st. If you updated your address after your renewal has already gone through, your box will still be shipped to the old address. Changes made after your renewal will only take affect with your next scheduled renewal. If you do need to update your address for the current month, please contact support@owlcrate.com before the 5th of the month. We will be able to update your address for you as long as your shipment hasn't been processed.

* Updating your Billing Address does not affect your Shipping Address.

settings.heading: When Will My Order Ship?
settings.txt:
Shop Orders:

Past boxes, books and other items purchased in the shop usually ship within 5-6 business days of being purchased. Once your order ships, you will receive an email with your shipping notification and tracking number. Please note that international shipments can take 5-7 business days to link up with the next stage of shipping so you may not see updates to your tracking link right away.

Subscription Boxes:

Our monthly subscription boxes generally ship between the 15th and 20th of each month. Once your box ships, you will receive an email with your shipping notification and tracking number. Delays can happen so be sure to check ourShipping Updates Page if you are curious about your shipment.

International boxes ship a bit earlier in the month as the process takes a bit longer, but you will receive an email with your shipping notification and tracking number around the time your box leaves the US, usually between the 15th and 20th.

Please make sure your shipping address on file is up to date before your next scheduled renewal, or emailsupport@owlcrate.comto get your current month's shipment updated before the 5th of the month. If you are contacting support after the 5th, we may or may not be able to update your address depending on the status of your shipment in our system.

settings.heading: Do You Ship To My Country?
settings.txt:
We currently ship to most countries* and though door-to-door tracking isn't offered in every country we ship to, almost everyone is able to subscribe!

Shipping rates vary depending on where you live. Shipping within the US is $8.99 USD per box.

You can find a list of our current International Shipping Rates in our Help Centre. You can find more information about tracking your shipment HERE.

* We don't currently ship to Mexico, Peru or Iran.

settings.heading: How Do I Skip A Box?
settings.txt:
If you are on themonthly planand would like to skip a box, you just need to log into your account and clickMANAGE SUBSCRIPTIONSorMy Subscriptions(both in teal).

On the next page, expand the active subscription box by clicking the[+]and you will then see theSKIP RENEWALoption on the left.

Be sure to skip before your renewal goes through on the 1st of that month. If you forget and a charge goes through, please email support@owlcrate.com as you will no longer be able to skip that box through your customer account.

If you are on the3-Monthor6-Month planand wish to skip a box, please emailsupport@owlcrate.com and we can skip your box for you.

If you skip a multi-month plan through your customer account, you will not be skipping one box but anentire 3- or 6-Month cycle.

For step-by-step instructions, please visit ourHelp Centre.

settings.heading: How Do I Cancel My Subscription?
settings.txt:
We're sorry to see you go but understand if you need to take a break!

To cancel your subscription, you just need to log into your customer account and clickMANAGE SUBSCRIPTIONSorMy Subscriptions. On the next page, you can expand the active subscription box by clicking the[+]. At the bottom right, you will seeMembership Options. You can cancel your subscription there.

Note: Cancelling only affects future renewals, it doesn't trigger an automatic refund.Any boxes that have already been paid for a time of cancellation will still be shipped. If you need to cancel any unshipped boxes, please email us at support@owlcrate.com.

settings.heading: Whats The Deal With Special Edition Books And Boxes?
settings.txt:
We love being able to offer Exclusive OwlCrate and OwlCrate Jr Books and Special Edition Boxes! These books and boxes are completely separate from our regular monthly subscription boxes and must be purchased individually through our shop.

Active subscribers will be sent an early access email, letting them know the date and time books/boxes will go on sale. If books/boxes havent sold out within the first 24 hours after going on sale, we will send the access link to everyone on our Newsletter List. After another 24 hours have gone by, we will open sales to the public if we have any remaining stock.

Special Edition Books and Boxes are a pre-order and will ship closer to the release date of the book itself. Details will always be noted in the shop listing. If it happens that you need to change the shipping address on your order, please contactsupport@owlcrate.comas soon as you can. Once your order ships, you will receive an email with your shipping notification and tracking number.

Please note that Special Edition Books and Boxes will show as SOLD OUT in the shop until the date and time they go on sale. All the information you need will be in the access email so be sure to read it carefully.

settings.process_txt:
We spend months reading hundreds of early manuscripts of upcoming young adult novels, and only select the very best books to include in our boxes! Each box will contain one brand new hardcover Young Adult novel, as well as 3-5 other bookish keepsakes to help set the mood for your literary adventure. settings.heading: What is OwlCrate?
settings.txt:
OwlCrate is a Young Adult book box designed for ages 14 and up. Each box contains a newly released hardcover novel which has an OwlCrate exclusive cover and is signed by the author. We also include 4-6 bookish goodies inspired by the book and other fandoms.

This box is not just for teens! We truly believe you are never too old to read YA!

settings.heading: How Much Does It Cost?
settings.txt:
We currently offer Monthly, 3-Month and 6-Month plans.

Monthly Plan = $32.99 USD per month plus shipping and applicable taxes.

3-Month Plan = $95.97 USD per 3-Month period plus shipping and applicable taxes.

6-Month Plan = $185.94 USD per 6-Month period plus shipping and applicable taxes.

Please note that all subscription plans are auto-renewing. Choose the GIFT option to avoid an auto-renewal.

Shipping within the US is $8.99 USD per box and you can find a list of International Shipping Rates HERE

settings.heading: When Do Your Monthly Boxes Ship?
settings.txt:
Our monthly subscription boxes typically ship between the 15th and 20th of each month. Once your box ships, you will receive an email with your shipping notification and tracking number. Delays can happen so be sure to check ourShipping Updates Pageif you are curious about your shipment.

International boxes ship a bit earlier in the month as the process takes a bit longer, but you will receive an email with your shipping notification and tracking number around the time your box leaves the US, usually between the 15th and 20th.

Please make sure your shipping address on file is up to date before your next scheduled renewal, or emailsupport@owlcrate.comto get your current month's shipment updated before the 5th of the month. If you are contacting support after the 5th, we may or may not be able to update your address depending on the status of your shipment in our system.

settings.heading: How Does The Waitlist Work?
settings.txt:
If we have temporarily sold out of subscriptions you will be directed to join our Wait List. When you join the Wait List, you will receive an email confirming you are on the list.

Once new subscription spots become available, we will start reaching out to those on the list, in small batches and in the order in which they joined. Within the email will be a special purchase link.

If we have contacted everyone on the list and there are still spots available, we will re-open the site to the public and you can purchase a subscription or gift through owlcrate.com.

Adding your email to this list doesn't reserve a box for you. If you change your mind after you have joined the list, you are under no obligation to buy a box - you can simply ignore the invitation to subscribe when it comes.

settings.heading: How Do I Know I Won't Already Own The Book You Send Me?
settings.txt:
The books we include in our boxes are published within 45 days of our monthly ship date. If you are in the habit of picking up new books on release day or pre-ordering anticipated titles, there is a chance you may receive a book you already have.

We usually drop a fairly big hint as to what our book will be in our monthly theme reveal, so if you need to skip a month, you can do so.

If you arent always purchasing new books, chances are you wont have the book we will be including.

settings.plan_caption: Subscribe to OwlCrate on a monthly, 3-month, or 6-month basis Dont worry, you can change or cancel your plan online at any time.

settings.txt:
OwlCrate was a dream born in a basement suite. Back in November 2014, Korrina and Robert set out to create a project that would bring readers around the world together. After a few months of planning and researching, the 'Magical Monthly Reads' concept was born and OwlCrate officially launched in February 2015 with incredible support from the Young-Adult book community. We mailed out our first box in March, and it's been an amazing ride ever since.

Thanks to our great subscribers and the book-community as a whole, in the course of just six months, we outgrew our basement-suite and had to find a new packing facility. Our boxes are now lovingly assembled by a family-run fulfillment team out of Portland, OR. They are a tight-knit group who do a fabulous job building all of our magical boxes every single month. By the end of the year Korrina and Robert had to quit their day jobs so they could dedicate themselves entirely to OwlCrate.

2016 brought on a whole new set of adventures! We participated in YallWest (Santa Monica, CA), BEA/BookCon (Chicago, IL) and the Texas Teen Book Festival (Austin, TX), where we had the chance to meet many wonderful OwlCrate subscribers in person. We also brought on more book lovers to our OwlCrate team, creating a brilliant group of customer service superstars.

We are so grateful to everyone who has supported us along our journey. We couldn't have done this without you and you are the reason we are able to live our dreams. We have so many thrilling ideas for the future of OwlCrate and we can't wait to see what you all think! Whether you've been with us since the very beginning (hey Mom!), or you've only just discovered us, we thank you.

settings.heading: What is OwlCrate Jr?
settings.txt:
OwlCrate Jr is an award-winning monthly subscription book box that delivers newly published hardcover novels and a collection of bookish goodies to your doorstep. Our original OwlCrate boxes are designed for ages 14+ and OwlCrate Jr is our Middle Grade box, designed for readers ages 8-12, or anyone young at heart!

We understand that it can sometimes be tough to get kids to pick up a book instead of turning on a screen, which is why we carefully curate every box to encourage curiosity, creativity, and imagination. Each one includes a brand new hardcover middle grade novel; an exclusive letter and signed book or bookplate from the author; a cool activity, game, or additional book; plus an assortment of fun goodies related to their theme of the month. Best of all, they ship right to your door starting at only $29.99 a month. Whether you have a voracious young bookworm in your life or are looking for a fun way to encourage a reluctant reader, OwlCrate Jr is the perfect low tech subscription for kids.

settings.heading: Who Is OwlCrate Jr Recommended For?
settings.txt:
OwlCrate Jr is our Middle-Grade box designed for kids of any gender ages 8-12. Our main monthly books tend to lean towards a higher reading level, making them great independent reads for strong readers or fun read-alouds for younger or new readers.

If your reader is in-between ages for our Middle Grade and our original YA box, we recommend taking a look through our Past Boxes section to see which feels like a better fit! If you would like to see the previous books and items we have included, please visit thePast Jr Boxessection atowlcrate.com.

Please make sure your shipping address on file is up to date before your next scheduled renewal, or emailsupport@owlcrate.comto get your current month's shipment updated before the 5th of the month. If you are contacting support after the 5th, we may or may not be able to update your address depending on the status of your shipment in our system.

settings.heading: Can I order just one box instead of a renewing subscription?
settings.txt:
You can definitely purchase a one-time box! There are three options to choose from:

1. Purchase a Monthly Subscription.

With this option, you can sign up for a regular monthly subscription through the main website. Once your order has gone through, you can log into your customer account and cancel your subscription. Cancelling won't affect the box you just purchase, only future renewals. The upside of this option is that if you love your first box (which we hope you do!), you can easily log into your account and reactivate your subscription to receive more boxes.

3. You can purchase a past box (while quantities are available) in our ONLINE SHOP!

settings.heading: What Is OwlCrate Jr?
settings.txt:
OwlCrate Jr is an award-winning monthly subscription book box that delivers newly published hardcover novels and a collection of bookish goodies to your doorstep. Our original OwlCrate boxes are designed for ages 14+ and OwlCrate Jr is our Middle Grade box, designed for readers ages 8-12, or anyone young at heart!

We understand that it can sometimes be tough to get kids to pick up a book instead of turning on a screen, which is why we carefully curate every box to encourage curiosity, creativity, and imagination. Each one includes a brand new hardcover middle grade novel; an exclusive letter and signed book or bookplate from the author; a cool activity, game, or additional book; plus an assortment of fun goodies related to their theme of the month. Best of all, they ship right to your door starting at only $29.99 a month. Whether you have a voracious young bookworm in your life or are looking for a fun way to encourage a reluctant reader, OwlCrate Jr is the perfect low tech subscription for kids.

settings.heading: Who Is OwlCrate Jr Recommended For?
settings.txt:
OwlCrate Jr is our Middle-Grade box designed for kids of any gender aged 8-12. Our main monthly books tend to lean towards a higher reading level, making them great independent reads for strong readers or fun read-alouds for younger or new readers.

If your reader is in-between ages for our Middle Grade and our original YA box, we recommend taking a look through our Past Boxes section to see which feels like a better fit! If you would like to see the previous books and items we have included, please visit thePast Jr Boxespage!

settings.faq_question: What are my reward credits eligible towards?
settings.faq_answer: Your reward credits/rewards are eligible towards online purchases with OwlCrate.
You will receive an email at the end of each month summarizing your rewards!

settings.faq_question: How many rewards can I earn in a month?
settings.faq_answer: You will earn one reward per month, the highest reward you qualify for, plus any bonus rewards (when applicable).

settings.faq_question: Can I get rewarded on any other social platforms?
settings.faq_answer: While you are more than welcome to share on other platforms, we are only offering rewards for Instagram at the moment.

settings.faq_question: Are Instagram stories included? What about IGTV's and Reels?

settings.faq_question: What if I didn't receive my reward?
settings.faq_answer: Please contact support@owlcrate.com and we can help you out!

settings.faq_question: How do I ensure my post is valid?
settings.faq_answer: Ensure you are posting from a public account, tagging @owlcrate, and following the post guidelines!
Once you have signed up just post and tag @owlcrate! Your posts will be automatically tracked. The more you post and tag @owlcrate, the more rewards you can earn!

settings.faq_question: Can I earn rewards for posting about OwlCrate Jr?
